  "title": "HR Talent Acquisition (Entry level, Central)",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Overview</strong></u></p><p>We are looking for talent aquisition/HR recruiters who are keen to shape their own career! Building on the remarkable reputation our household brand – Recruit Express & winning new businesses. Opportunities are plentiful here!</p><p><u><strong>Position Overview</strong></u></p><p>• We are looking for quick thinking, innovative, motivated Recruitment Consultants with demonstrated technical agility to work with our team to help evolve, maintain, troubleshoot and support our recruitment and platform users.</p><p>• Employees are rewarded and recognized based off performance and results.</p><p>• Real advancement opportunities based off performance.</p><p>• The selected candidate will develop and implement strategic recruiting plans to hire top talent in a highly competitive talent market</p><p><u><strong>Responsibilities</strong></u></p><p>• Lead full cycle recruitment processes and managing the candidate experience from end to end.</p><p>· Interview and assess potential candidates</p><p>· Identify potential candidates using a variety of sourcing channels<br /><br />· Carry out business development activities & build rapport with both new & existing clients</p><p>· Improve and guide new hires through the on-boarding program</p><p>· Participate in company events and assist in campus outreach</p><p>• Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned</p><p><u><strong>Get to Enjoy</strong></u></p><ul><li>Annual company bonding events and quarterly motivational workshops</li><li>Great incentives for your dedicated hard work</li><li>Cohesive divisions with great team spirit</li><li>Comprehensive Training</li><li>Dynamic Working environment</li><li>Exciting opportunities to develop a rewarding career</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p><ul><li>Min. Degree in any field of study.</li><li>Strong interest in marketing and/or business development</li><li>Applicants with good track record in sports or other co-curricular activities in school will have an added advantage</li><li>Possess optimism, enthusiasm and most importantly, passion for people</li><li>On the job training provided!</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>We regret to inform that only shortlisted applications will be contacted.</strong></p><p>Interested applicants, please apply directly/email your updated CV to reina.ng@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>EA Personnel No: R21103938</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Reina Ng Hwee Min</p><p>Company Registration Number: Recruit Express Services Pte Ltd (13C6614)</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p>",
